Digital Services for Nonprofits

In collaboration with Childlife Preserve Shishur Sevay, we believe that every nonprofit—no matter how small or under-resourced—deserves a strong digital presence to amplify their mission and connect with the world.

Through our Digital Services for Nonprofits initiative, we provide free website support, digital tools, and strategic guidance to grassroots organizations working for social impact.

💼 What We Offer:

  • Website Design & Hosting – A professional online home to share your work.

  • Custom Domain & Email Setup – Build trust with branded communication tools.

  • Basic SEO & Social Media Guidance – Reach your audience more effectively.

  • Digital Literacy Support – Training so your team can manage and grow online.

🤝 Who This Is For:

  • New and small nonprofits without digital infrastructure

  • Rural and community-based organizations needing visibility

  • Volunteer-led or cause-based groups working on limited resources
